Project Title: Bad Bank
Description/Motivation: Banks are bad, but with the power of MERN, I will be making them not so bad
Installation Guidelines: 
- Go to the project directory
- In the terminal, type in `npm install`, and press return
- Then enter `node index.js` and press return. Ensure that port 3000 is not being used by any active applications.
- Go to `https://localhost:3000` in your browser
- Start banking
Screenshots: Screenshots or a GIF of your project in action.
Technology used: 
- Frontend - React JS
- Backend - Node JS
- Application Framework - Express JS
- Database - MongoDB
- Authentication - Firebase
